<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/113576.The_Smartest_Guys_in_the_Room"><img alt="The Smartest Guys in the Room: The Amazing Rise and Scandalous Fall of Enron" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1309204701l/113576._SX98_.jpg" />
